Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,还没来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我来晚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我出发了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.42,0:00:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好的 拜托你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要把开膛手杰克…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好 出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.57,0:00:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,请稍微放轻松一点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,之后我们可是要当诱饵的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我会努力的
